query:
SELECT
                number,
                l1_tx_count,
                l2_tx_count,
                timestamp
            FROM
                l1_batches
            LEFT JOIN
                via_l1_batch_inscription_request
                ON l1_batches.number = via_l1_batch_inscription_request.l1_batch_number
            WHERE
                commit_l1_batch_inscription_id = $1
                OR commit_proof_inscription_id = $1
